-- Centrotherm Photovoltaics Unit Wins Coating Systems Order From Solarion
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-11-15T09:00:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/centrotherm-photovoltaics-unit-wins-coating-systems-order-from-solarion.html
Centrotherm Photovoltaics AG’s FHR
Anlagenbau GmbH unit has won an order to supply “several”
roll-to-roll coating systems to Leipzig, Germany-based Solarion
AG. The order is worth a “double-digit” amount in millions of
euros, Centrotherm said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  